PrecisAppointment of Gail Scott, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; designation of the said Gail Scott for the Ontario region, as established under subsection 10(1.1) of that Act; and determine that she shall reside within 100 kilometres of the Ontario regional office, effective April 19, 1993.
